<p><span style="font-size: small;">It's a privilege to have the Rev. Dr. Marilyn Sewell as our guest on Episode 20.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: small;">For 17 years, Marilyn served as the Senior Minister of the First Unitarian Church of Portland, Oregon, before retiring and being named Minister Emerita.</span></p>
